      <item>Task 009 (depends on task 007 ordering) asserts each error path here.</item>
    </related-work>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Rigor Declaration">
      Output: 🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL · 📋 REASON: code-impl in BFF (.cs file modification, tag bff-api, FR-13 validation contract is semantically load-bearing — Playbook Builder UI consumes the messages directly) — quality gates Step 9.5 required · Proceeding with Step 0...
