    <step order="4" name="Implement Validate() body">
      Replace the task-002 Validate() skeleton with the FR-13 contract. Use the goal list above as the literal error-message text (precise wording matters — UI consumes these). Aggregate all errors into a single List&lt;string&gt;; return Failure(list.ToArray()) if any, else Success().
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Add brief XML doc on Validate()">
